	<body style="background-color:#F2EBCF">
		<font color="#00574B"><b>Author</b></font>
		<br>
		Emre Üsküplü
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#00574B"><b>About WeatherApp</b></font>
		<br>
		You can see weather of your location and you can add bookmarks with google map to see their weather.
		<br>
		You can see detailed weather and forecast weather days of your location or bookmarks.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#00574B"><b>Using WeatherApp</b></font>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">Home Page</font>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> Your location weather at top side in home page.
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can open the map via (
		<img src="file:///android_res/drawable/add_location.png" width="25" height="25">
		) button for adding bookmarks.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can open your location detailed weather via click your location weather image or temp degree.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can open your bookmarks detailed weather via click atop bookmarks in list.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can search bookmarks with their location name via magnifying glass button.
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can refresh weather via (
		<img src="file:///android_res/drawable/refresh.png" width="25" height="25">
		) button.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can delete your bookmarks in list with swipe to right.
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can open settings page via (
		<img src="file:///android_res/drawable/settings_flat.png" width="25" height="25">
		) button.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">Map Page</font>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can adding bookmarks with keep pressing 2 seconds on map.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">Detailed Weather Page</font>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can see detailed weather of forecast days via click atop them.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can change the page with swipe in bookmarks detailed weather.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">Settings Page</font>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can switch units of your weather values with metric or fahrenheit.
		<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#008577">&gt</font> You can delete all your bookmarks.
	</body>
</html>